    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後　新MVの撮影日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれから優と瑠依で話し合って、瑠依は）\n（音楽番組の最終回に出ることにした訳だが……）",
      "startTime": 5.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.2962358475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、本当に晴れやかな顔をしているな\n無事に意見がまとまったようで、何よりだよ",
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8195694924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに言われた通り\nうちの気持ちを踏まえて、話したおかげです",
      "startTime": 19.430735629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "トリエル三人で活動したいのは、うちも一緒や",
      "startTime": 23.4122903824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.0149662336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "でもその上で、今回は瑠依ちゃんには\n特番に出てもらいたい、って伝えたんよ",
      "startTime": 30.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、瑠依ちゃんになんて言われたと思います？",
      "startTime": 34.6356011709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8287756444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて言われたんだ？",
      "startTime": 38.8287756444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "今回の特番を逃したとしても絶対にまた\n同じぐらいに実績を作ってみせるから、って",
      "startTime": 44.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.552380681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今回はみんなが一番納得出来る方法を\n選んでみよう、って",
      "startTime": 52.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで結局、最終回にはみんなで\n出ることにしたんだな",
      "startTime": 57.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.5943535089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うちは、自分の気持ちを我慢してでも最善の道を\n進むべきやって思っとったんやけどなぁ",
      "startTime": 63.9276302576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うちが我慢しなくても済むような最高の道を\n三人で一緒に切り開けばいい",
      "startTime": 71.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6116781791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "なんて瑠依ちゃんに言われたら、断れへんよ",
      "startTime": 74.6116781791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "三人ならそれが出来るって、瑠依ちゃんは信じてる\nなら、うちはそれを叶える方法を探さな",
      "startTime": 83.5654530227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8186849038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "最終回が大いに盛り上がって\n裏番組すら超える最高の道を",
      "startTime": 90.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "それがTRINITYAiLEのブレーンにして\n瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんの親友、鈴村優の役目です",
      "startTime": 97.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.053197058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。なら俺も、可能な限り協力しないとな\nTRINITYAiLEのマネージャーとして",
      "startTime": 107.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.0807481051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、頼りにさせてもらいます\nふふ、頼んでおいた新しい衣装も準備してくれはったし",
      "startTime": 113.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんが、裏番組に出た方が良かった、って\n言われないように。胸を張って誇れるように――",
      "startTime": 122.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7147387743
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "三人で、力一杯羽ばたいてみせますから\n見守っていて下さいね",
      "startTime": 130.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（悩みが晴れたからか）\n（今日の優はなんだか楽しそうに見えるな）",
      "startTime": 137.1653109901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "（デビューしたばっかりの時は）\n（うちらは雛鳥みたいなもんやった）",
      "startTime": 142.9666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、三人で支え合い、頑張ったからこそ）\n（うちらはこんなにも高く飛べるようになった）",
      "startTime": 150.7999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "（一人じゃこんなところまで来れへんかった）\n（二人がいてくれたからこそ、今のうちがある）",
      "startTime": 158.1999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "（だから、絶対に辿り着くって決めたんや）\n（誰も知らない道の先まで――）",
      "startTime": 167.0333272297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽番組最終回の数日後",
      "startTime": 171.0612875858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 172.5879654803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "結局、うちらが出た番組は\nあの特番に視聴率で負けてもうたね",
      "startTime": 176.8000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど、SNSのトレンドはうちらが独占や\nふふ、頑張った甲斐あったなぁ",
      "startTime": 185.2000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "優は新しい衣装のアイデアを出したり、最終回用の企画\nを先方に提案したり、本当に頑張ってくれていたからな",
      "startTime": 192.5427403847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "そういう{user}さんこそ\n頑張ってくれてはったやん",
      "startTime": 199.1868405188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんから聞いたで。うちのことだけやなくて\n瑠依ちゃんのこともフォローしてくれてはったんやろ？",
      "startTime": 205.7666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうな。今回、トリエルが前に進めたのは\n{user}さんのおかげや",
      "startTime": 214.4666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺はマネージャーとして当たり前のことをしただけだよ\n優達の頑張りがあったからこそだ",
      "startTime": 220.2666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
